Package: xactonomial
Type: Package
Title: Improved Small-Sample Inference for Real-Valued Functions of Multinomial Parameters from k-Samples 
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2025-04-14
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Michael C",
             family = "Sachs",
